downloadTitle: Office 2016 Help Files: Office Fluent User Interface Control Identifiers
downloadDescription: This download contains files for and information about each of the control IDs for built-in UI commands and menu items in all applications that use the Office 2016 Fluent UI.
detailsSection: These names are also accessible within the Office 2016 products by hovering over controls in the QAT customization dialog box, and looking at the tooltip of the control. To get the latest control identifiers for Office 365 applications, please visit https://github.com/OfficeDev/office-fluent-ui-command-identifiers.
systemRequirementsSection:
This download contains Excel files with the relevant information. After downloading, you will need one of the following to read the files:
  • Microsoft Excel 2016
  • Microsoft Excel 2013
  • Microsoft Office Excel 2010
installInstructionSection:
Download the .zip file, open or save it, and then view any of the Excel files contained in it.

Instructions for use:
Open any of the files that are contained in Office2016FluentUserInterfaceControlIdentifiers.zip and view them by using Excel 2016, Excel 2013, or Excel 2010 as you normally would.

Remove of this download:
There is no removal feature for this download.
additionalInformationSection: This package does not collect any personal information.
